{"tid":698831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依家睇番轉頭，金正恩先喺下緊最大盤棋","createTime":"2018-06-12T04:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T05:54:58.000Z","uid":102643,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"24c5b88eefe86cca01fb0e69274c699705311371","tid":698831,"uid":102643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:58:08.000Z","msg":"早幾年新聞：<br />\n北韓「攝政王」張成澤被處以死刑，對於張的死法眾說紛紜。網上有傳言指，他被處以「犬決」，遭餓狗生吞下肚，北韓領導人金正恩還率領妻子李雪主及300名高官全程觀看。 <br />\n<br />\n有傳言指，張成澤被扒光衣物，關進大牢裡，官方找來120條餓了3天的東北獵犬，放入張成澤身處牢內，將張生吃下肚，過程持續1小時，金正恩帶李雪主和高官全程在旁觀看。 <br />\n<br />\n過往流傳，金正恩對付異己的手法兇殘，去年有指他為鞏固權力，在黨政軍內大清算，一名軍官被指在哀悼已故領袖金正日期間飲酒作樂，被金正恩下令用迫擊炮處決，炸至粉身碎骨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金正恩用唔同藉口殺曬班舊黨，樹立暴君形象，個時舊登，全世界都話佢殘暴過金正日，原來只係要為左準備開放北韓做準備。呢幾年佢繼續研究核武，應該只係唔想浪費咁多年人力物力，雖然比全世界鬧佢極權，一搞掂完，即時開放北韓，停戰。<br />\n<br />\n相比強國個位，不得不讚肥仔恩先係真正嘅棋靈王，下左咁大盤棋咁耐，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50dba7895f201bb34e770999ae4efa7d1c21c20","tid":698831,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37d807b469dcb7c06f8caf2c8a173981c29a04ea","tid":698831,"uid":19552,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"根本係最屈機80後"},{"pid":"b381ccfa888a3ac750bcca33f36b7e758e4e4013","tid":698831,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:01:01.000Z","msg":"金正恩勁過腥港班狗官"},{"pid":"b1e5dc13b0efa6e59106bbb0326d32a4094ae5c5","tid":698831,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37d807b469dcb7c06f8caf2c8a173981c29a04ea","tid":698831,"uid":19552,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"根本係最屈機80後"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:25:22.000Z","msg":"真係。。。無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b1be5f97d5e392db93d0255c7453094ecf6abd","tid":698831,"uid":25038,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"喺你老母"},{"pid":"7d107e948c1cf7e66cf193a9eebf89636ee8d2bd","tid":698831,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:28:00.000Z","msg":"Trump: 習近平是世界級撲克玩家"},{"pid":"4eaa68f75b412694db3c35f23d1cd477cbc22be2","tid":698831,"uid":106348,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:30:38.000Z","msg":"話晒接受過西方教育，思想比較開放唔出奇<br />\n<br />\nbtw肥仔都有人吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d53111d8b64af9865ed831f7cd920b4fd421b7","tid":698831,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"喺乜春呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"2c7e966f20198aa1e82112b34fda5fc4600b8d3f","tid":698831,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:49:42.000Z","msg":"中國咪又係最大嬴家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4edd10f2f4569741ddc2982de1ec78b83a9d45f6","tid":698831,"uid":28800,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:13:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a8cfc558a1a18d57a78e1d826e604bb163dc875","tid":698831,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:16:57.000Z","msg":"如果咁講<br />\n最初其實應該估唔到班友真係整到粒核彈<br />\n整唔到就一鑊處決班友<br />\n整到就帶去見美國總統談判<br />\n點知整完核彈仲整到氫彈<br />\n爭啲玩出火<br />\n跟住 2018 元旦即轉口風<br />\n唔覺得佢轉得好急咩？"},{"pid":"0e1140801d0ab492ab2e44b50edb9496e209a878","tid":698831,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:22:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支那幾千年優良DNA：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">馬後炮！！！！！</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"000e63611b7aafa37787ab9d46500393b18cd665","tid":6